snippet.title: Cris Tales Characters Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase
snippet.description:
Meet Crisbell and her companions in the official Cris Tales character trailer! 

Cris Tales will be available on Switch, PC, PlayStation, Xbox and Stadia this July!

#CrisTales
